{"tid":53833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【札幌大風雪】滯留3日終歸家 港航旅客:好辛苦好似難民","createTime":"2016-12-25T04:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T11:04:09.000Z","uid":987,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca10f515a19a4ad27e3700135401c5f61b5c2f5d","tid":53833,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"【12:10更新】旅客劉小姐形容，滯留在新千歲國際機場，如難民一樣。<br />\n<br />\n日本北海道札幌新千歲國際機場，受大風雪影響一度關閉﹝<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2irFC8I﹞，滯留航機今陸續啟航，但由於受影響旅客實在太多，有待消化。其中香港航空一班原定22號(周四\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2irFC8I%EF%B9%9E%EF%BC%8C%E6%BB%AF%E7%95%99%E8%88%AA%E6%A9%9F%E4%BB%8A%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E5%95%9F%E8%88%AA%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E7%94%B1%E6%96%BC%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E5%AF%A6%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%85%E6%B6%88%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%80%E7%8F%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%AE%9A22%E8%99%9F%28%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B&d=FQIZZSg3jStbvmcjSHMLoGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=2020437f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2irFC8I﹞，滯留航機今陸續啟航，但由於受影響旅客實在太多，有待消化。其中香港航空一班原定22號(周四</a>)返港的旅客，滯留近3天至今日凌晨終於可以起飛，並於早上8時56分抵港。<br />\n參加東瀛遊6天團的劉小姐，與母親同行，卻在北海道遇上半世紀最大的暴風雪。劉說：「第一晚瞓機場，第二晚住酒店，今朝凌晨再出機場登機。」她形容在機場等候的時間「好辛苦、好似難民咁。」機場禁區內有兩間便利店，「要同成個機場嘅人爭，所有食物飲品都被掃清光，連飲水機都冇水」，其後出境才可以補充糧水。<br />\n劉又說，拿住行李喼出出入入，特別吃力和疲倦，「如果有地方存放，會好好多」。她指，出發前購買了旅行社指定的保險，酒店費用可以索償，航空公司亦每人賠1,200元，不過實在太辛苦太難忘，「短期內都唔去札幌」。<br />\n同機的另一位旅客薛小姐指，滯留至今日凌晨4時終於啟程，全機200多名乘客於早上近9時抵達赤鱲角機場。乘客們對於終於能回家感到如釋重負，薛小姐表示:「好攰、好攰」，她謂港航給予每人1,200元賠償。<br />\n想睇最新消息？　即時follow【現場－蘋果突發】fb！<a href=\"http://fb.co/applecitycrime\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.co%2Fapplecitycrime&d=FQIZZSg3jStbvmcjSHMLoGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=9f89e173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.co/applecitycrime</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161225/56090446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161225%2F56090446&d=FQIZZSg3jStbvmcjSHMLoGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=af9323fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161225%2F56090446&h=15527b6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161225/56090446</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161225/large/1482639232_3420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161225%2Flarge%2F1482639232_3420.jpg&h=5258dd3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉小姐與母親在日本遇大風雪滯留，今早終於返抵香港。(簡明恩攝)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed70cc6304a359f568599bcd4f7baeed082880b","tid":53833,"uid":31713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"喱班人可唔可以唔好柒"},{"pid":"60b7eea6c43fd1abbfc75902a5793d82334884a2","tid":53833,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"小小事都唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193ca9e2d00bd72c0783fc854790cc7f5fe827e0","tid":53833,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:48:10.000Z","msg":"風雪delay，其實好閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1496a527410ec3849be5a01112b15c1a5fef4a6b","tid":53833,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2